/obj/item/paper{
	pixel_x = -5;
	pixel_y = 7;
	name = "Lizard's Gas Food Menu";
	color = "#6D6D6D";
	default_raw_text = "<table width=100% bgcolor=DarkGreen><tr><th><font color=white size=10><center></center></font></th></tr><tr><th><font color=white size=8><center>Lizard's Gas®</center></font></th></tr><tr><th bgcolor=MediumOrchid><font color=white size=5><center><p>Food Menu</center></font></th></tr><tr><th><font color=white size=4><center></center></font></th></tr></table><hr><br>Welcome to your local Lizard's Gas Service Station! We offer plenty of services here, including food, drink, and medicine.<br>Below is our menu for the food we have available, please let us know what you'd like to buy!<br><br><hr><table width=100% bgcolor=DarkGreen><tr><th><font color=white size=3><i><b>№  Name & Price</b></i></font></th></tr></table><hr><br><b><u>COMBOS</u></b><br>• Engine Kickstarter: Five pastries¹, two snacks, and a drink - all for only 100 credits!<br>• Full Refuel: Main Course², two sides, one snack/pastry, and one drink, all for only 120 credits!<br><br><b><u>Burgers</u></b><br>01. Burger: 40 credits<br>02. Cheese Burger: 50 credits<br>03. Bacon Burger: 50 credits<br>04. Fish Burger: 60 credits<br>05. Chicken Burger: 60 credits<br>06. Crab Burger: 80 credits<br>07. Big Bite Burger: 90 credits<br>08. Big Blue Burger: 300 credits<br>09. Sloppy Moe: 80 credits<br>10. McRib: 70 credits<br>11. McGuffin: 70 credits<br>12. Rootburger: 50 credits<br>13. Chicken Rootwich: 60 credits<br>14. Fish Rootburger: 70 credits<br>15. Root-Guffin: 80 credits<br>16. Sssloppy Moe: 90 credits<br><br><b><u>Hotdogs & Sandwiches</u></b><br>17. Hotdog: 50 credits<br>18. Danish Hotdog: 60 credits<br>19. Sandwich: 60 credits<br>20. Grilled Cheese Sandwich: 50 credits<br>21. Philly Cheesesteak: 60 credits<br>22. BLT: 60 credits<br><br><b><u>Sides</u></b><br>23. Fries: 15 credits<br>24. Cheesy Fries: 20 credits<br>25. Izakaya Fries: 20 credits<br>26. Wild Duck Fries: 25 credits<br>27. Salt N' Chilli Fries: 20 credits<br>28. Poutine: 20 credits<br>29. Onion Rings: 15 credits<br>30. Chicken Nuggets (6): 40 credits<br>31. Fried Chicken: 20 credits<br>32. Nachos: 15 credits<br>33. Cheesy Nachos: 20 credits<br>34. Cuban Nachos: 25 credits<br>35. Garlic Bread: 20 credits<br><br><b><u>Salads</u></b><br>36. Antipasto Salad: 70 credits<br>37. Caesar Salad: 70 credits<br>38. Greek Salad Salad: 70 credits<br>39. Herb Salad: 50 credits<br>40. Kale Salad: 60 credits<br>41. Potato Salad: 60 credits<br>42. Valid Salad: 60 credits<br><br><b><u>Pastries & Dairies</u></b><br>43. Donuts (any): 30 credits<br>44. Jelly Donuts (any): 40 credits<br>45. Cornuto: 30 credits<br>46. Icecream Sandwich: 30 credits<br>47. Yoghurt: 30 credits<br><br><b><u>Others</u></b><br>48. Fish and Chips: 40 credits<br>49. Refried Beans: 50 credits<br>50. Mashed Potatoes: 50 credits<br>51. Sausage with Eggs: 30 credits<br>52. Omelette Du Fromage: 40 credits<br>53. Canned Tomatoes: 20 credits<br>54. Canned Beans: 20 credits<br>55. Canned Peaches: 20 credits<br>56. Canned Tuna: 20 credits<br><br><b><u>Hemophage Specials</u></b><br>57. Boat Noodles: 50 credits<br>58. Dinuguan: 80 credits<br>59. Blood Soup: 60 credits<br><br><b><u>CHAP Specials</u></b><br>60. CHAP: 50 credits<br>61. Chappy Patty: 70 credits<br>62. Chap Hash: 70 credits<br>63. Chapsilog: 70 credits<br><br><b><u>Snacks</u></b><br>64. Candy Bar: 20 credits<br>65. Sticko Biscuit (any): 25 credits<br>66. Chocolate Bar: 25 credits<br>67. Chips (any): 20 credits<br>68. Boritos (any): 20 credits<br><br>We can do takeaway, just ask!<br><br><hr><font color=DarkGrey size=1><i><b>¹Can also be any dairy product.</b></i></font><br><font color=DarkGrey size=1><i><b>²Items from the Burgers, Hotdogs/Sandwiches, Salads, Others, and CHAP Specials - excluding the Big Blue Burger.</b></i></font><br><hr><table width=100% bgcolor=DarkGreen><tr><th><font color=white size=3><center>How to ensure a pleasant visit</center></font></th></tr></table><hr><br>During your visit to Lizard's Gas, it is paramount to maintain a pleasant and civil environment, so please keep in mind the following:<br>• Be kind to the employees of Lizard's Gas! While they might be here to serve you, they are still people, and treat them as such.<br>• If you are still unsure what to order, please leave the line and re-queue once you do figure out your order. The time of the employees and other customers is valuable!<br>• Do not litter the service station,<br>• Not all items will always be available, we apologize!<br>• Please return any utensils after finishing your food.<br>• Don't forget to pay! Lizard's Gas has an active 24/7 surveillance camera system.<br>• Do not attempt to enter the staff only areas.<br>• Do not assault any other customer or employee, verbally or physically.<br><br><hr><table width=100% bgcolor=DarkGreen><tr><th><font color=white size=10><center>Lizard's Gas®</center></font></th></tr></table>";
	desc = "Strange, what is the menu of Lizard's Gas doing here?"
	},
/obj/item/paper{
	pixel_x = 0;
	pixel_y = 4;
	name = "Lizard's Gas Drinks Menu";
	color = "#4A8ED5";
	default_raw_text = "<table width=100% bgcolor=DarkGreen><tr><th><font color=white size=10><center></center></font></th></tr><tr><th><font color=white size=8><center>Lizard's Gas®</center></font></th></tr><tr><th bgcolor=MediumOrchid><font color=white size=5><center><p>Drinks Menu</center></font></th></tr><tr><th><font color=white size=4><center></center></font></th></tr></table><hr><br>Welcome to your local Lizard's Gas Service Station! We offer plenty of services here, including food, drink, and medicine.<br>Below is our menu for the drinks¹ we have available, please let us know what you'd like to buy!<br><br><hr><table width=100% bgcolor=DarkGreen><tr><th><font color=white size=3><i><b>№  Name & Price</b></i></font></th></tr></table><hr><br><b><u>Smoothies</u></b><br>01. Berry Blast: 20 credits<br>02. Strawberry Banana: 20 credits<br>03. Vanilla Dream: 20 credits<br>04. Funky Monkey Smoothie: 20 credits<br>05. Gibb Floats: 20 credits<br><br><b><u>Sodas</u></b><br>06. Space Cola: 15 credits<br>07. Dr. Gibb: 15 credits<br>08. Melon Soda: 15 credits<br>09. Pwr Game: 15 credits<br>10. SM Wind: 15 credits<br>11. Sol Dry: 15 credits<br>12. Soda Water: 10 credits<br><br><b><u>Non-carbonated</u></b><br>13. Coffee: 20 credits<br>14. Iced Coffee: 25 credits<br>15. Cafe Latte: 25 credits<br>16. Soy Latte: 25 credits<br>17. Tea: 10 credits<br>18. Iced Tea: 15 credits<br>19. Juices (any): 15 credits<br>20. Water: 5 credits<br><br><b><u>Alcoholic²</u></b><br>21. Space Beer: 30 credits<br>22. Vodka: 80 credits<br>23. Fernet: 120 credits<br><br>We can do takeaway, just ask!<br><br><hr><font color=DarkGrey size=1><i><b>¹All drinks can be upsized to large, at double price (Normal: 50u, Large: 100u).</b></i></font><br><font color=DarkGrey size=1><i><b>²The sale of alcohol requires an ID to be presented, alcohol won't be sold to those below the age of 21.</b></i></font><br><hr><table width=100% bgcolor=DarkGreen><tr><th><font color=white size=3><center>How to ensure a pleasant visit</center></font></th></tr></table><hr><br>During your visit to Lizard's Gas, it is paramount to maintain a pleasant and civil environment, so please keep in mind the following:<br>• Be kind to the employees of Lizard's Gas! While they might be here to serve you, they are still people, and treat them as such.<br>• If you are still unsure what to order, please leave the line and re-queue once you do figure out your order. The time of the employees and other customers is valuable!<br>• Do not litter the service station,<br>• Not all items will always be available, we apologize!<br>• Please return any utensils after finishing your food.<br>• Don't forget to pay! Lizard's Gas has an active 24/7 surveillance camera system.<br>• Do not attempt to enter the staff only areas.<br>• Do not assault any other customer or employee, verbally or physically.<br><br><hr><table width=100% bgcolor=DarkGreen><tr><th><font color=white size=10><center>Lizard's Gas®</center></font></th></tr></table>";
	desc = "Strange, what is the menu of Lizard's Gas doing here?"
	},
/obj/item/paper{
	pixel_x = 5;
	pixel_y = 1;
	name = "Lizard's Gas Medical Menu";
	color = "#C35D5B";
	default_raw_text = "<table width=100% bgcolor=DarkGreen><tr><th><font color=white size=10><center></center></font></th></tr><tr><th><font color=white size=8><center>Lizard's Gas®</center></font></th></tr><tr><th bgcolor=MediumOrchid><font color=white size=5><center><p>Medical Menu</center></font></th></tr><tr><th><font color=white size=4><center></center></font></th></tr></table><hr><br>Welcome to your local Lizard's Gas Service Station! We offer plenty of services here, including food, drink, and medicine.<br>Below is our menu for the medical options we have available, please let us know what you'd like to buy!<br><br><hr><table width=100% bgcolor=DarkGreen><tr><th><font color=white size=3><i><b>№  Name & Price</b></i></font></th></tr></table><hr><br><b><u>First Aid</u></b><br>01. Red Sun Balm: 25 credits<br>02. Ointment: 30 credits<br>03. Sealed Aseptic Gauze: 25 credits<br>04. Regenerative Mesh: 75 credits<br>05. Hemostatic Mesh: 50 credits<br>06. Bruise Pack: 50 credits<br>07. First Aid Bandages (Six Pack): 100 credits<br>08. Sutures: 50 credits<br>09. Hemostatic Sutures: 75 credits<br>10. Coagulant-F Packet: 50 credits<br>11. Rapid Coagulant Applicator: 100 credits<br>12. Medical Gauze: 20 credits<br>13. Bone Gel: 40 credits<br>14. Surgical Tape: 40 credits<br>15. Subdermal Splint Applicator: 100 credits<br><br><b><u>Medicines</u></b><br>16. Bruise Patch: 50 credits<br>17. Burn Patch: 50 credits<br>18. Synthflesh Patch: 150 credits<br>19. Amollin Painkiller: 20 credits<br>20. Iron Pill: 15 credits<br>21. Probital Pill: 40 credits<br>22. Epinephrine Pill: 40 credits<br>23. Convermol Pill: 40 credits<br>24. Multiver Pill: 40 credits<br>25. Potassium Iodide Pill: 30 credits<br>26. Insulin Pill: 30 credits<br>27. Psicodine Pill Pill: 50 credits<br>28. Ondansetron Pill: 50 credits<br>29. Sansufentanyl Pill: 50 credits<br>30. Mannitol Pill: 75 credits<br>31. Neurine Pill: 100 credits<br>32. Albuterol Canister: 150 credits<br><br><b><u>Autoinjectors</u></b><br>33. Occuisate Sensory Restoration Injector: 100 credits<br>34. Calopine Emergency Stabilizant Injector: 100 credits<br>35. Halobinin Soberant Injector: 100 credits<br>36. Synthetic Cleaner Autoinjector: 100 credits<br>37. Synthetic Smart-Solder Autoinjector: 100 credits<br><br><b><u>Bloodpacks¹</u></b><br>38. Regular Types: 50 credits<br>39. Universal (O-) Type: 75 credits<br><br><b><u>Synth Meds</u></b><br>40. Robotic Repair Patch: 25 credits<br>41. Robotic Repair Spray: 150 credits<br>42. Premium Robotic Repair Spray: 250 credits<br><br>Purchases above 300 credits come with a free frontier medical kit!<br><br><hr><font color=DarkGrey size=1><i><b>¹If unsure of your own blood type, please purchase O- blood or consult to a medical doctor first. Lizard's Gas® is not legally responsible to how the customer uses bloodpacks and/or medicines.</b></i></font><hr><table width=100% bgcolor=DarkGreen><tr><th><font color=white size=3><center>How to ensure a pleasant visit</center></font></th></tr></table><hr><br>During your visit to Lizard's Gas, it is paramount to maintain a pleasant and civil environment, so please keep in mind the following:<br>• Be kind to the employees of Lizard's Gas! While they might be here to serve you, they are still people, and treat them as such.<br>• If you are still unsure what to order, please leave the line and re-queue once you do figure out your order. The time of the employees and other customers is valuable!<br>• Do not litter the service station,<br>• Not all items will always be available, we apologize!<br>• Please return any utensils after finishing your food.<br>• Don't forget to pay! Lizard's Gas has an active 24/7 surveillance camera system.<br>• Do not attempt to enter the staff only areas.<br>• Do not assault any other customer or employee, verbally or physically.<br><br><hr><table width=100% bgcolor=DarkGreen><tr><th><font color=white size=10><center>Lizard's Gas®</center></font></th></tr></table>";
	desc = "Strange, what is the menu of Lizard's Gas doing here?"
	},
