/obj/structure/rack,
/obj/item/paper{
	pixel_x = 9;
	pixel_y = -6;
	default_raw_text = "Great news folks, your station was picked as the lucky team to test out the brand new selection that our R&D boys been working on, you may be able to recognize a brand or two there, but do not worry. I been reassured by our legal team that the modifications we have made are perfectly legal for commercial use, as long as you <B>DO NOT</B> resell those boards. Anyway, try out those bad boys, they were designed to make each station completely self-sufficient and not have to rely on infrequent shipments to remote locations, and completely turns any medical issues experienced inside the gas stations into the sole responsibility of the staff within and not the chain as a whole, <B>innovation!</B><BR><BR>-Supply Manager, Jasper 'Jas' Statham";
